&lt;p&gt;A post has become available within the KMPT Estates, Facilities and Capital Planning team for a confident individual with excellent communication and customer service skills who will provide a professional first point of contact for our 24/7 centralised switchboard.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post offers an excellent opportunity to work in a busy and diverse role. The successful candidate will need to be flexible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;37.5 hours per week on a rota system, working Monday-Sunday – Shifts 6am-2pm, 2pm-10pm &amp; 10pm-6am, including all bank holidays.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If your application is successful you will be notified by e-mail and advised to check your NHS Jobs account. Therefore, please ensure that you regularly check both your email and your NHS Jobs account.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Completed applications by: 19th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
